                            <comment id="15874385" author="chetanm" created="Mon, 20 Feb 2017 11:13:22 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Added ignored test in 1783740. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15874394" author="cziegeler" created="Mon, 20 Feb 2017 11:20:09 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The escaping of the writer is correct, a slash can be espaced - it&apos;s not a must though - some libs do, others don&apos;t. So I think this needs to be handled in the parser&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15874410" author="chetanm" created="Mon, 20 Feb 2017 11:37:23 +0000"  >&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;escaping of the writer is correct, a slash can be espaced - it&apos;s not a must though&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://stackoverflow.com/questions/1580647/json-why-are-forward-slashes-escaped&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://stackoverflow.com/questions/1580647/json-why-are-forward-slashes-escaped&lt;/a&gt; also confirms that. FWIW org.json.JSONObject did not escaped the slash but its done by other libraries&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15874411" author="reschke" created="Mon, 20 Feb 2017 11:38:07 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Indeed, see &amp;lt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://greenbytes.de/tech/webdav/rfc7159.html#rfc.section.7&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://greenbytes.de/tech/webdav/rfc7159.html#rfc.section.7&lt;/a&gt;&amp;gt;:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;   string = quotation-mark *char quotation-mark

   char = unescaped /
       escape (
           %x22 /          ; &quot;    quotation mark  U+0022
           %x5C /          ; \    reverse solidus U+005C
           %x2F /          ; /    solidus         U+002F
           %x62 /          ; b    backspace       U+0008
           %x66 /          ; f    form feed       U+000C
           %x6E /          ; n    line feed       U+000A
           %x72 /          ; r    carriage return U+000D
           %x74 /          ; t    tab             U+0009
           %x75 4HEXDIG )  ; uXXXX                U+XXXX

   escape = %x5C              ; \

   quotation-mark = %x22      ; &quot;

   unescaped = %x20-21 / %x23-5B / %x5D-10FFFF
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15880515" author="bosschaert" created="Thu, 23 Feb 2017 14:27:00 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I can take a look at fixing this soon if nobody else beats me to it...&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15882549" author="bosschaert" created="Fri, 24 Feb 2017 12:12:22 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Should be fixed in &lt;a href=&quot;https://svn.apache.org/viewvc?view=revision&amp;amp;revision=1784269&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://svn.apache.org/viewvc?view=revision&amp;amp;revision=1784269&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I added a few additional tests as well.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
